00:19:10.690 --> 00:19:12.470
Consegues?

00:19:14.660 --> 00:19:16.250
Oh, meu deus.

00:19:16.350 --> 00:19:17.670
Consegues?

00:19:18.530 --> 00:19:19.810
Bebé: Sim.

00:19:20.510 --> 00:19:22.280
- Uau!
- Uau!

00:19:22.640 --> 00:19:24.260
